snippet.textDisplay: Wow, completely disgusted with Super Showdown.  Old wrestlers bury all the young talent.  This is coming from a die hard Undertaker fan.  This last match though was the worst of them all.  You spend a year building up this amazing character to have him be squashed by Oldberg?  No storyline build up, Fiend looks previously indestructible, and then bury him....again? (see wrestlemania 33)  You think a guy who gets gassed after 5 minutes and can't even perform his finisher properly deserves to headline Wrestlemania?  You really think the WWE universe want to see Goldberg vs. Reigns??? You are extremely out of touch with your fan base.  I've been a WWF/WWE fan all my life, over 30 years, and for the first time I'm considering switching to AEW or shutting off wrestling completely.  I strongly suggest you fix this before Mania, you should be ashamed of yourselves.
